.:: Puzzle 6x2-Level-1-2::.
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: november, september
The people have 2 different hobbies: camping, filmmaking
House: tower, townhouse
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: folk, pop
2 different pets are kept: bird, rat
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: rose, dahlia
1. the fan of pop is on the right of the owner of the rat##1
2. the person who's birthday is in september is the fan of pop##1
3. the tower house is on the left of the person who's hobby is camping##1
4. the person who growsrose is on the left of the owner of the bird##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |
| Birthday      | november        | september   |
| Hobby         | filmmaking | camping |
| House   | tower     | townhouse   |
| Music-Genre   | folk       | pop     |
| Pet           | rat        | bird    |
| Flower     | rose  | dahlia    |

