The people have 2 different hobbies: baking, writing
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: martial-arts, superhero
The people use 2 different means of transport: trike, subway
2 different pets are kept: cat, guinea-pig
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: bongani, pall-mall
1. the owner of the cat is on the left of the person who's hobby is baking##1
2. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the right of the person who's birthday is in october##1
3. the person driving the subway is on the left of the bongani-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2       |
| Birthday          | october    | november      |
| Hobby         | writing   | baking       |
| Movie-Genre   | superhero | martial-arts |
| Transport   | subway  | trike    |
