2. the bolivar-smoker is on the right of the fan of indie##1
3. the person driving the helicopter is on the left of the bolivar-smoker##1
4. the person watching musical movies is on the right of the fonseca-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |
| Cigar          | fonseca        | bolivar  |
| Hobby         | rock-climbing | drawing    |
| Transport           | helicopter        | train |
| Movie-Genre   | fantasy       | musical    |
| Music-Genre   | indie       | salsa    |
| Sport         | baseball      | parkour    |

